{"tid":650259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞刀賊闖7仔　截劫印度漢2萬元金鏈及現金","createTime":"2018-05-02T07:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T07:48:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53aaceca988c3534dd7acb2eeb320fe04f519e7d","tid":650259,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:25:07.000Z","msg":"南亞兵團又作奸犯科，便利店外截劫同鄉！現場油麻地寶靈街8號地下7-11便利店，凌晨1時許，一名29歲印度男子SINGH，與2名南亞裔及一名本地男友人到上址購買飲品後，甫出門口時，遭一名南亞裔男子截停，並用鎅刀指嚇SINGH，趁機搶去其身上穿戴的一條約值16,000港元金鏈，與及載有4,000港元銀包，得手後逃去，事主報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n事主及友人俱無受傷，其後由警員陪同乘坐警車兜截無發現，返回現場助查。警方亦進入便利店調查及向職員了解情況，並根據現場天眼片段追緝在逃賊人，他身高約1.6米、瘦身材。案發時戴鴨舌帽及口罩，身穿藍色上衣及藍色牛仔褲，案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"7b970f824e5c2e1d5badf392d1f416ef341cb282","tid":650259,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180502/photo/bkn-20180502023323122-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180502130557\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180502%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180502023323122-0502_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180502130557&h=79b872e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f47854853ce955f2dbed489a2c45268e7e32309","tid":650259,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:26:38.000Z","msg":"差佬個樣仲斯文個受害者..."},{"pid":"5c2b221916f15f594df8e8e151cc5074f80447f3","tid":650259,"uid":37733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:26:42.000Z","msg":"近排d好nice既南亞人去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21da16943a75bf25be7e70d285a17dd5271b03db","tid":650259,"uid":86673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0cb754a13526c9e6370bd91add598502e15ef3","tid":650259,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":